name: Palm on the shoulders
description:
In month of Muharram people of our village do many rituals, one of the important ones in desert part of Iran is carrying Nakhl. Nakhl is a symbolic representation of a cuffin, it's a wooden structure and there are fabrics and mirrors attached to it. Here you can see men of the village, carrying the Nakhl on their shoulders.
